{"id":"korhites","term":"Korhites","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A Levitical family descended from Korah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Exodus 6:24\">Ex. 6:24</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 12:6\">1 Chr. 12:6</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 26:1\">26:1</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 20:19\">2 Chr. 20:19</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Exodus 6:24","1 Chronicles 12:6","1 Chronicles 26:1","2 Chronicles 20:19"]}